<dl>
    <dt>Ensure the device is not suspended</dt>
    <dt>From a supplementary device, call the SUT</dt>
        <dd>Incoming call shall be notified on screen with option to answer or ignore</dd>
        <dd>If the calling number is in the addressbook and if the number isn't hidden by the operator, the callers name shall be displayed; if not, the phone number when not hidden by the operator</dd>
        <dd>External speaker shall provide feedback on ring</dd>
    <dt>Select the answer button</dt>
        <dd>Voice shall be bidirectional</dd>
    <dt>End call from originator</dt>
        <dd>Repeat by ending call from target</dd>
</dl>
<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
